Test-System
- using mocha
- using should.js

Install:
  install nodes.js 
  > sudo npm install -g mocha
  > sudo npm install -g jsdom should cssstyle htmlparser2 nwmatcher jquery
  > export NODE_PATH=/usr/local/lib/node_modules
  
Usage:
  mocha 
or 
  mocha -w -R min

-----------
Code couverage:
Install:
  npm install -g istanbul
  
usage
  istanbul cover _mocha --dir ./test/coverage -- -R spec
